Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.39,0:00:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\N Just Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.71,0:00:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.92,0:00:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.72,0:00:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:01:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.44,0:01:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.75,0:01:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.96,0:01:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉財團藉著\N邀請和平的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.56,0:01:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.30,0:01:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為財團的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到人們的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.14,0:01:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令世界國家實現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.01,0:01:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面，在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反抗OZ殖民地式支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稱為白色獠牙的武裝市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.78,0:01:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在各個衛星紛紛起義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.58,0:01:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了獨立運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰亂的時代繼續進一步加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.56,0:02:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨大變動的一剎那即將出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那傢伙死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界國家和這種虛假的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.70,0:02:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就能被消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.78,0:02:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.71,0:02:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十話\N[新的領導人]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.45,0:02:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們整理現狀看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.32,0:02:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.72,0:02:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉正利用\N莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.69,0:02:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,統一其勢力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.36,0:02:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜是否反過來利用羅姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.80,0:02:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但地球總算開始\N朝著和平起步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.24,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是開始變得混沌的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙裡有五股勢力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼多勢力嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有，首先是白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是最大的問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎樣處置從OZ手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.59,0:02:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶過來的那艘巨大戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們正繼續建造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想在和OZ宇宙軍的戰鬥裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好使用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.09,0:03:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為OZ宇宙軍是另一股勢力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙佔上風也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙要塞巴爾吉也還健在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.87,0:03:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以上兩者的戰鬥\N是更大的問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有...向以上兩者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.28,0:03:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展開游擊戰的鋼彈們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.58,0:03:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道其他的兩股勢力是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兩者在稱為勢力方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.32,0:03:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍為沒有力量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.05,0:03:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一股是附和白色獠牙\N的衛星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在人數上是最多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們沒有表明意願的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組織性和力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一股是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.80,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.23,0:03:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據傑克斯的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要和鋼彈們聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，傑克斯那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了地球後為何還不回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.75,0:04:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球正步向新的和平時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們服從莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖放低武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼是和平?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們打算奪去我們的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續確立OZ的支配體制吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.69,0:04:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消滅擾亂和平的兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.64,0:04:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!別怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈果然是幫我們消滅OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈為何會幫游擊隊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.86,0:05:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜，身在羅姆斐拉之內的妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟只會產生虛假的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉或許會奪去我的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.30,0:05:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我甚至或許會被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.84,0:05:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.94,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉會利用我繼續戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在確立世界國家方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.29,0:05:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說妳有一套方針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在，羅姆斐拉被認為是一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.69,0:05:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以武力支配人們的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是無可奈何的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉首先須要向人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.97,0:06:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展示正確和平的應有狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.07,0:06:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳說出具體方案莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把派到世界各地維持治安的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.78,0:06:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ軍力全部撤去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有異議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後，高聲宣佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.82,0:06:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武力支配結束的時代來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有異議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不說那其實是\N膚淺的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看來沒想到散佈各地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游擊隊或獨立國家的軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.90,0:06:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會成為我們的威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威脅其實是羅姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支配一方呼籲拋掉武器時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.91,0:06:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支配者自己一定要先拋掉武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎?莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.51,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是羅姆斐拉財團所希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.75,0:06:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支配世界的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從為世界帶來和平的立場來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉財團也到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.29,0:06:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要改變的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.46,0:07:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有傳統的我們根本沒必要改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.43,0:07:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你個人的想法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.87,0:07:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是整個羅姆斐拉的想法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉整體的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.44,0:07:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算代言呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.91,0:07:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.45,0:07:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我們還未達到意見統一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.89,0:07:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜女王的意見也有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說羅姆斐拉會因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個女孩的話而改變嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我或許說得過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想各位注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉今後的方針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只憑莉莉娜女王的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.28,0:07:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而決定的話會有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議題只是議題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在明天的財團總會裡討論吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.56,0:08:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最高幹部會到此為止，散會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.29,0:08:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只好放棄五飛那傢伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.43,0:08:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙打算獨自迎戰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，回地球一次嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙的部隊散佈在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.74,0:08:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強行突破會很困難吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.58,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說就此不管白色獠牙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.42,0:08:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該能令地球和宇宙和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.68,0:08:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後再和白色獠牙談判就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N白色獠牙一直繼續武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.56,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然衛星的人不可以拿起武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是暗號通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.26,0:08:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是從這附近的空域傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訊息裡有死神這字眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪歐，你聽到嗎?迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.68,0:08:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍華大叔嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.91,0:08:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看在以前的情誼上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.28,0:09:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會再次僱用我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.28,0:09:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,補給和修理我當然也會承包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍華你為何會在宇宙啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連財團的主要幹部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.13,0:09:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不聽我的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.33,0:09:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家想服從那個莉莉娜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.07,0:09:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那就是莉莉娜陛下的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為了鞏固OZ的團結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才拉攏莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣子她就變成障礙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.05,0:09:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果莉莉娜陛下\N現在有甚麼不測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺你首先會被懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.25,0:09:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，現在的爺爺你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.56,0:09:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有說服大家的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一針見血，桃樂絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，妳講得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,財團正在動搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.10,0:09:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強大的領導人\N一定要團結所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.07,0:10:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為團結OZ和民眾的象徵就夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.38,0:10:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜陛下的和平路線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也認為不會就此順利被接納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會需要武力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.52,0:10:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直維持著羅姆斐拉軍力的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.05,0:10:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會大家認同為強大的領導人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.33,0:10:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜正想把\N羅姆斐拉的軍力解體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.66,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺你不是有OZ的宇宙軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.47,0:10:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫我去宇宙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在明天的財團總會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.91,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺你的意見不會通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.44,0:10:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家會同意\N莉莉娜陛下的意見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起打那種必輸的仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.72,0:10:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該準備軍力應付下一場仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳打算怎辦?桃樂絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會留在莉莉娜陛下身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.93,0:10:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她身邊，戰鬥的風暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定又會猛烈地颳起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到我在這年紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要做前線指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾麥優侯爵前往宇宙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.88,0:11:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名目是為了\N牽制抬頭的白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.42,0:11:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親自前去指揮OZ宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.35,0:11:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防範衛星叛軍，改變航路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.29,0:11:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到達巴爾吉的時間會比原定遲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧，笨蛋們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就証明給你們看\N我是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好極了，莉莉娜陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺前往宇宙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.12,0:11:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最反對的人不會出席總會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.26,0:11:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後只有看莉莉娜陛下妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.76,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?  迪爾麥優侯爵他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時候差不多了，莉莉娜陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去議事堂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是鋼彈?不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，相信是鋼彈05的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經衝破防衛網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現正接近這艘[天秤座]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.44,0:12:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈不是為了衛星而戰的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.81,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他為何攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以宇宙獨立為目標的我們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙不需要那種力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動所有部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於派了部隊去攻擊巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.29,0:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在，天秤座周圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎沒有護衛部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開動天秤座吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，天秤座還未…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.67,0:13:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲和推進裝置\N以外應該能開動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用天秤座的雷射砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位是全世界的領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，今後要繼續擔任領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.84,0:13:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉財團就一定要改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.95,0:14:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在，這個時代正繼續改革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對立為何不消失?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.89,0:14:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為異已的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.99,0:14:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經常會成為對立的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要令對立消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一定要所有人一條心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.83,0:14:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜，那很膚淺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再次宣佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了令對立消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建立和平的統一國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有最強力量的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先就要放下武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贏了!鋼彈失去蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.26,0:15:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，西迪茲上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.93,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們確認到宇宙還有數部鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.27,0:15:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們今後也有可能再次來襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈為何敵視我們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.51,0:15:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為鋼彈想為地球而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.28,0:15:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衛星的真正敵人是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣戰吧，上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.29,0:15:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.52,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們打算先消滅OZ宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正派遣部隊前去巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.53,0:15:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仍然難以代表衛星全體的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.13,0:16:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令衛星意思統一的好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.04,0:16:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是木偶也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.31,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不顧自己人的傷亡\N也要消滅敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一樣啊，那樣和OZ無分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.55,0:16:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是宇宙不需要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.12,0:16:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界統一並非只是包括地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.53,0:16:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩種個體會產生對立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.13,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要和宇宙合而為一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球和宇宙，宇宙和地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球和宇宙和平共存?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.34,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除OZ的武裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼籲宇宙和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望各位作為以往的領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受這次改革
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.42,0:16:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.33,0:17:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，希洛，殺死我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳，莉莉娜女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.33,0:17:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉財團會遵從妳而重生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.51,0:17:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，莉莉娜，妳做給我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會打倒我的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修理完畢後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠鋼彈也能在宇宙盡情戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你，霍華先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也需要機動戰士作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.33,0:18:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給予鋼彈駕駛員\N使用的機體方面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.83,0:18:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連重武裝鋼彈的下落還不明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我沒有記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.54,0:18:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…我不是那意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.94,0:18:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍華，我不明白的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為何援助我們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.38,0:18:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.65,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想用這艘艦做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也正為這問題而煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是甚麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.49,0:18:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，援助你們方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了履行責任啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.66,0:18:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為參予製造鋼彈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾參予製造鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是製造托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.27,0:18:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不知道\N傑克斯的下落嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.14,0:18:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於他，我認為他還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色獠牙有事向地球宣佈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是宣戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.58,0:19:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們衛星渴望和平地\N得到自治權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.99,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但地球總是以武力壓迫我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.66,0:19:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯合的時代是，OZ的時代是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.06,0:19:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而宣佈建立\N世界國家的地球也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.90,0:19:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球方面的先鋒是鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球方面使用鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.30,0:19:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊渴望宇宙統一的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.31,0:19:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了援助OZ宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.61,0:19:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能!那是藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被利用了，五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.75,0:19:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，OZ宇宙軍即將被消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經派遣大型部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.09,0:19:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進攻OZ宇宙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙是我們衛星居民的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是白色獠牙的大型部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.63,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何會在這空域?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全速離開!逃進巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.99,0:20:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行!會被追上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我在這種地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪…迪爾麥優侯爵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.45,0:20:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起，爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.79,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為爺爺你最後也在戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為勇敢的士兵而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙統一時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們剩下的敵人就是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有大義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.41,0:21:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，我們迎接了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貫徹那大義的新領導人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的領導人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球和宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.02,0:21:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個個體會產生對立吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.13,0:21:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.30,0:21:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和宇宙對立的個體，地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.17,0:21:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡宣佈要肅清它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.70,0:21:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會的?傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.24,0:21:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在連羅姆斐拉\N也想改變的這時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.01,0:21:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑克斯，從次代\N顯示的未來裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你選擇了那條路嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從飛翼零式顯示的未來裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇了的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.55,0:21:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.51,0:22:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.39,0:22:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.39,0:22:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.39,0:22:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.39,0:22:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.89,0:22:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.39,0:23:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.89,0:23:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.39,0:23:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.39,0:23:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.59,0:23:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜女王被特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.69,0:23:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從財團代表的寶座上推下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.23,0:23:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時，在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.66,0:23:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥終於爆發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.23,0:23:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是宇宙要塞-巴爾吉的攻防戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.33,0:23:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數目上佔優勢的白色獠牙軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.54,0:23:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穩健地壓倒OZ的MD部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.81,0:23:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第四十一話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.74,0:23:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾吉攻防戰
